Sentencas: Solid oxide fuel cells attract growing attention as an environmentally friendly device that can produce electrical power.
Titulo: A new design for co-extrusion dies: Fabrication of multi-layer tubes to be used as solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Many processing routes are available for fabrication of micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cells, among which extrusion can be considered as the most commonly used method.
Titulo: A new design for co-extrusion dies: Fabrication of multi-layer tubes to be used as solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Recently, a coextrusion process has been introduced, in which anode and electrolyte layers can be fabricated simultaneously, thus reducing the overall fabrication cost.
Titulo: A new design for co-extrusion dies: Fabrication of multi-layer tubes to be used as solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: In this study, a new die design for coextrusion of ceramic tubes is introduced in which 5 different layers can be fabricated by a single processing step and can be used for fabrication of micro-tubular solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: A new design for co-extrusion dies: Fabrication of multi-layer tubes to be used as solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Moreover, an integral model developed for pressure drop in different flow fields of the die.

Sentencas: Summing up the pressure drops, the pressure drop in the whole process can be calculated.

Sentencas: The SEM images show that the co-extrusion process can be performed successfully and the tube consists of 5 distinct layers.
